          "date": "2013-01-29 17:09:55.000000000",
          "tz": -480
        },
        "subject": "LU-2158 fsfilt: Rename and modify fsfilt_ext3.c",
        "message": "LU-2158 fsfilt: Rename and modify fsfilt_ext3.c\n\nThis change replaces the fsfilt_ext3.c file with it's fsfilt_ldiskfs.c\ncounterpart. Previously this was done dynamically using a complex\nsolution of autoconf variables, make targets, and scripting. Now that\nfsfilt_ldiskfs.c is a \"real\" source file in the tree, much of the lvfs\nbuild system complexities are unnecessary and have been removed.\n\nAdditionally, this is a precursor to removing the lvfs directory\naltogether. When that happens, the fsfilt_ldiskfs.c file can be\nmoved into the ldiskfs OSD layer as a stop gap solution until its\nfunctionality is no longer needed.\n\nSigned-off-by: Prakash Surya <surya1@llnl.gov>\nChange-Id: I76931670ad1f2ce2ada5a305ffde3f40df5dcd7f\n"
      },
      "branch": "refs/heads/master"
    }
  },
